    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/aa56ea5331644653f1911c65f256c8e5.poster.avif?t=1747814088\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/aa56ea5331644653f1911c65f256c8e5.webm?t=1747814088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/aa56ea5331644653f1911c65f256c8e5.mp4?t=1747814088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>“魔女的庭院”</strong>是一款将美妙的感情和精美的动作相结合的roguelike游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使遇到困难也不轻言放弃，才能拯救“庭院”。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她正在等待着你…… </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >魔女们需要举办茶会！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/3e288ec29479db991332f7d4703d3986.poster.avif?t=1747814088\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/3e288ec29479db991332f7d4703d3986.webm?t=1747814088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/3e288ec29479db991332f7d4703d3986.mp4?t=1747814088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>“庭院”面临着坍塌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一切都是因为那些缺乏危机意识、不守约的懒惰魔女们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔女的“庭院”就这样被毁灭，看起来似乎是一个合理的因果报应，但至少我们的主人公“茜尔”并不愿意看到这样的结果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了守护好不容易建成的小窝，为了不让&quot;庭院&quot;被毁灭，到了该行动的时刻。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >庭院很危险。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/42bb3a520b2ad45ec1bf959c78beede5.poster.avif?t=1747814088\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/42bb3a520b2ad45ec1bf959c78beede5.webm?t=1747814088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/42bb3a520b2ad45ec1bf959c78beede5.mp4?t=1747814088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请使用在各个关卡中获得的能力击败怪物，并“说服”难搞定的魔女们乖乖参加“茶会”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就算中途被打倒也无需担心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事并不会发生改变，但有机会获得更强的力量后再次挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在温馨小窝里提高能力，调整战略重新出发吧！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作方法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持Xbox，PlayStation等大部分控制器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以直接使用键盘进行游戏，无需鼠标。（方向键、Z、X、C、A、D、Space、Tab、Esc）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>请点击、“添加至您的愿望单”，支持“魔女的庭院”吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/70695bfc853ee39e70d3eb5609eed0f1.poster.avif?t=1747814088\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/70695bfc853ee39e70d3eb5609eed0f1.webm?t=1747814088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187780/extras/70695bfc853ee39e70d3eb5609eed0f1.mp4?t=1747814088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
